{"tid":1189014,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"淺談中世紀魔女狩獵","createTime":"2019-06-06T15:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T13:04:40.000Z","uid":105678,"like":482,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c0b678cf3c252cac886784fbaa9a6a70395cca","tid":1189014,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"中世紀魔女狩獵(下稱獵巫)，係沿自於12世紀嘅一項人類傳統文化，特指有拖行巫術、魔法嘅人被人捉上宗教法庭審判嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>異端裁判所(Inquisition)</strong><br />\n<br />\nInquisition係由羅馬天主教所設立嘅司法機關，係12至13世紀嘅初期，初期主要負責審理嘅案件，包括家庭糾紛、褻瀆上帝等行為。女巫、男巫等狩獵行為仍然未係佢地嘅主要職責，<br />\n<br />\n異端裁判所作為獨立司法機關，直屬於教庭。審判過程嘅主要參與者有：法官、詢問官、律師以及被告人。同現代制度不同嘅係，當時律師嘅職務主要係說服被告人認罪，因為當時嘅文化認為上得庭就一定係有罪，法官咁正直，點會冇啦啦告鳩你 ?<br />\n<br />\n<strong>處刑</strong><br />\n<br />\n到14世紀中期，裁判所正式成為獵巫機關，同女巫獵人通力合作，齊齊獵巫。由於異端裁判所嘅有罪推定，佢地慢慢學識咗點樣逼人認罪，同埋如何係處刑中令樂見其成嘅民眾從中得到快樂<br />\n<br />\n而處刑嘅方法包括：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/amenra0131/4aa86fb61c9e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Famenra0131%2F4aa86fb61c9e9.jpg&h=0cd8324c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>火刑</strong>，將罪人用草編繩綁係刑架上，然後點火。其中有部份會直接用鐵釘釘死手手腳腳，避免火刑期間草繩燒斷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.renminbao.com/rmb/article_images/2016/05/31/160531zhende03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.renminbao.com%2Frmb%2Farticle_images%2F2016%2F05%2F31%2F160531zhende03.jpg&h=545f620d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接受呢項處刑中最出名嘅人物，法國聖女：貞德<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gushi.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Fig-11.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgushi.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FFig-11.gif&h=270130e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>絞刑</strong>，一般人所接受嘅刑罰，最方便同節省成本，係當時偏遠嘅地方非常流行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.minutemediacdn.com/image/upload/c_fill,g_auto,h_1248,w_2220/f_auto,q_auto,w_1100/v1555927072/shape/mentalfloss/trialbyordeal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.minutemediacdn.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fill%2Cg_auto%2Ch_1248%2Cw_2220%2Ff_auto%2Cq_auto%2Cw_1100%2Fv1555927072%2Fshape%2Fmentalfloss%2Ftrialbyordeal.jpg&h=46bf0dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>水刑</strong>(Trial by Water)，直譯係水的考驗，將被告嘅手手腳腳綁住掉入河中，如果浮得上來，佢就係得到魔鬼嘅保護，該殺。如果浮唔上嚟，就證明佢係正常人。<br />\n<br />\n不過最好笑嘅無論結果點樣，被告人都係要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285a9969afb0d972daaf80314dcc68531b426770","tid":1189014,"uid":186844,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"少有高汁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f644e40eeebc46aaeb8aaa92f241cdfa70ecb2e0","tid":1189014,"uid":105678,"like":284,"dislike":6,"score":278,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"好興幸我出生係21世紀，竟然仲見證到人類文化嘅傳承，有得一齊玩獵巫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309521361f7be386bfa9184c0933b29b66680720","tid":1189014,"uid":52358,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"quote":{"pid":"f644e40eeebc46aaeb8aaa92f241cdfa70ecb2e0","tid":1189014,"uid":105678,"like":284,"dislike":6,"score":278,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"好興幸我出生係21世紀，竟然仲見證到人類文化嘅傳承，有得一齊玩獵巫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:26:55.000Z","msg":"獵毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbe0946c410d38167b106c0bffe8a02c420a5e7","tid":1189014,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"309521361f7be386bfa9184c0933b29b66680720","tid":1189014,"uid":52358,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"quote":{"pid":"f644e40eeebc46aaeb8aaa92f241cdfa70ecb2e0","tid":1189014,"uid":105678,"like":284,"dislike":6,"score":278,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"好興幸我出生係21世紀，竟然仲見證到人類文化嘅傳承，有得一齊玩獵巫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:26:55.000Z","msg":"獵毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci